'''Owerri''' bụ ịsị óche [[Imo State]]. Dika ịsị óche ndi ewere na obodo [[Naigeria]], '''Owerri''' were ọtụtụ madu bi n'ime ya.
Owerri ugbua were ụlọ akwukwo di elu nke mere ya obodo akwukwo, ulo akwukwo ndia bu Federal university nke owerri, Federal polythenic nke Nekede, Imo state university ya na Alvan Ikoku college nle education di kwa na owerri. ulo akwukwo ndia emepela Owerri ya were buru ebe aguma akwukwo di mma.
  

